Sar-chluicheadair ceolmhor aig [[Led Zeppelin]], gu h-abhaisteach, chluicheadh e am bass ach bha e sgileil le iomadach ionnstraimeadan eile.  As deidh dha Led Zeppelin a sgaradh, fhuair e cliu mar riochdire sgoinneil don leithid de [[R.E.M.]] agus [[Na Butthole Surfers]].  The e air da chlar a chlaradh leis fhein, [[Zooma]] agus [[The Thunderthief]].
